#### glar_panel - LED panel controller

glar_panel - LED panel controller

Commands:

nnn         3-LED bitmap, n is 0 or 1 left to right
,           Pause for 100msec
;           Pause for 500msec
.           Pause for 100msec if inactive
:           Pause for 500msec if inactive
*           Repeat previous sequence

